  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I am hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only thing I want to be with you, but I can't write so much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If the oceans were ink and the skies paper, I couldn't describe the horror of what I'm going through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it's quite a long letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In our company, those picture book of the killed children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I just want to say even children were killed there, which I mentioned already, which I saw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the big blessing for me-- the big blessing for me is that I'm here alive and able to talk about it and remembering.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I hope so that never ever something like that will happen again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we are through now, almost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so, like I say, it was the third winter-- cold and freezing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We already had some knowledge that the end of the war is soon coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we probably won't see it-- freedom-- ever because the SS there in our kommando, where we had better condition than the rest, promised that the only way to freedom for us is through the chimney and pointed at it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were sure we never will survive because [? we ?] special-- knew too much and saw too much.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
